    "summary": "Energy consultant combining technical solutions, local circumstance and business strategy towards a feasible energy infrastructure business case with full involvement of stakeholders. Familiar with power, heat and cold solutions, both renewable and fossil based, small and large scale. Structured approach in strategy or project development. Aiming at reducing energy need in the first place, secondly using excess energy available in the neighborhood followed by optimal development of local renewable energy sources. Finally topped up with external renewable energy and high efficiency fossil fuel applications. It is all about the perfect combination of production, transport, storage and use of energy. Over time interest increased is sustainable concepts liked bio based economy and circular economy thus bringing energy and resource management together. Key skills: sound technical background, knows how to manage a development from first idea to a feasible business case, loves working together with different stakeholders, transfer knowledge and present insights in workshops and on conferences.",
